title: The Best Vacuum Seal Bags & Rolls
description: When it comes to vacuum storage bags there's good reason why the FoodSaver brand is the best. FoodSaver Vacuum Seal bags are made with BPA-free, multi-layer protection to keep food fresh up to 5X longer and prevent freezer burn. These extremely durable, yet pliable bags create an airtight barrier around foods and are safe for use in the microwave, refrigerator, freezer and sous vide cooking.
